.TH PRODBOX_vault 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-vault \- Vault secret-management lifecycle
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox vault
.SH DESCRIPTION
The in-cluster Vault lifecycle: seal-status, init, unseal, reconcile, key rotation, and PKI inspection. The host-side encrypted unlock bundle (.data/prodbox/vault-unlock-bundle.age) recovers a torn-down cluster's Vault.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBstatus\fR
Report Vault seal state
.TP
\fBinit\fR
Initialize Vault
.TP
\fBunseal\fR
Unseal Vault
.TP
\fBseal\fR
Seal Vault
.TP
\fBreconcile\fR
Reconcile Vault policy
.TP
\fBrotate-unlock-bundle\fR
Re-encrypt the unlock bundle
.TP
\fBrotate-transit-key\fR
Rotate a Transit key
.TP
\fBpki\fR
Vault PKI inspection
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox vault status\fR
Probe the in-cluster Vault seal state.
